Package: QTLseqr
Type: Package
Title: QTL mapping using Bulk Segregant Analysis of Next Generation Sequencing data
Version: 0.7.5.2
Date: 12-3-2017
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ben Nathan", "Mansfeld", email = "mansfeld@msu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Rebecca", "Grumet", email = "grumet@msu.edu", role = c("ths"))
    )
BugReports: https://github.com/bmansfeld/QTLseqr/issues
Description: QTLseqr performs QTL mapping using Bulk Segregant Analysis of Next Gen Sequencing data. The package is an R implementation of the analyses described in Magwene PM, Willis JH, Kelly JK (2011) The Statistics of Bulk Segregant Analysis Using Next Generation Sequencing. 
